claim.claim-text:
An adhesion flange structure comprising:
a first flange extending along an end portion of a first vehicle body panel, and formed at the end portion of the first vehicle body panel with a bend portion interposed therebetween;
a second flange formed at an end portion of a second vehicle body panel that configures a section of a vehicle body together with the first vehicle body panel, the second flange formed facing the bend portion and the first flange;
an adhesive that adheres the bend portion and the first flange to the second flange; and
a ridge projection portion formed extending along a direction in which the first flange extends at the end portion of the first vehicle body panel, and formed to at least one portion out of the bend portion and a facing portion of the second flange that faces the bend portion, the ridge projection portion forming a projection towards the opposing side out of the bend portion and the facing portion.
